Wasu 'yan majalisa sun ji tsoron shawarar da aka yi na canja sunansu zuwa MWP (Member of the Welsh Parliament  ɗan majalisa na Wales).
An gabatar da wannan shawara ne dangane da shirin sauya sunan majalisa zuwa Majalisa ta Wales.
'Yan majalisa daga jam'iyyun siyasa daban-daban suna tsoron cewa hakan zai iya kawo ba'a.
Wani dan majalisa na jam'iyyar Labour ya ce jam'iyyarsa na damuwa cewa kalmar '' ta yi karo da kalmomin twp da pwp.
Ga masu karatu daga waje: a yaren Welsh twp na nufin wawa kuma pwp na nufin shaye-shaye.
Wani dan majalisa na jam'iyyar Wales ya ce jam'iyyar baki daya ba ta gamsu ba kuma tana ba da shawarwari.
Wani dan majalisa na jam'iyyar Conservative ya ce jam'iyyarsa na shirin sauya sunan liberal.
A wannan mahallin, ana furta haruffan Welsh w kamar u.
A yanzu haka, kwamitin majalisar yana aiki a kan wani kudiri na dokar da zai kawo sauye-sauyen sunaye, inda ya ce: Tabbas, 'yan majalisar ne za su yanke shawara na ƙarshe game da yiwuwar nada 'yan majalisar.
Dokar Gudanar da Wales ta 2017 ta ba wa Majalisar Tarayyar Wales ikon canza sunanta.
