'Yan sanda sun kama wanda ake zargi da kisan dan wasan LSU, Dytone Simpson
'Yan sanda sun kama wanda ake zargin ya harbe Wayde Sims, dan wasan kwando dan shekara 20 na LSU.
An kama mutum mai suna Dyteon Simpson, 20, kuma an tsare shi a kan laifin kisan kai na mataki na biyu, in ji sashen 'yan sanda na Baton Rouge.
Hukumomi sun fitar da bidiyo na yadda Sims da Simpson suka yi faɗa, kuma 'yan sanda sun ce Sims ya rasa tabarau sa'ad da suke faɗa.
