Bayan an yi wa Simpson tambayoyi, 'yan sanda sun ce ya yarda cewa ya harbe Sims.
A cewar mai gabatar da kara, an sanya belin sa a kan dala 350,000.
Ofishin likitan shari'a na yankin East Baton Rouge ya bayar da rahoton farko na mutuwar a ranar Juma'a, inda ya ce an kashe shi ne sakamakon harbin da ya yi masa a kai da kuma wuyansa.
Sashen ya gode wa rundunar 'yan gudun hijirar 'yan sandan jihar Louisiana, da dakin binciken masu aikata laifuka na 'yan sandan jihar, da 'yan sanda na jami'ar Southern University da kuma 'yan unguwar saboda taimakon da suka bayar a binciken da ya kai ga kama mutumin.
Daraktan wasannin LSU Joe Alleva ya gode wa hukumomin shari'a na garin saboda kokarinsu na tabbatar da adalci.
Sims yana da shekara 20.
Dan wasan mai tsayi 198 ya girma a Baton Rouge, inda mahaifinsa Wayne ya buga kwando a LSU.
A kakar wasan da ta gabata, ya kai maki 5.6 da kuma kwallaye 2.6 a kowane wasa.
A safiyar Juma'a, kocin kwando na LSU, Will Wade, ya ce kungiyar ta yi matukar bakin ciki da kuma mamakin mutuwar Sims.
"Wannan shi ne abin da kuke tsoro akai-akai", in ji Wade.
