Kamar yadda kasar Sin ke kara samun karfi a fannin kere kere, Amurka za ta ninka kudaden da take kashewa wajen bincike a fannin, in ji mai zuba jari da kuma mai tallata kere kere Kai-Fu Lee, wanda ya yi aiki a kamfanonin Google, Microsoft da Apple.
Wannan ya biyo bayan wasu jami'an gwamnatin Amurka da suka yi tsokaci kan batun na'urar kere kere, duk da cewa Amurka ba ta da wata dabara ta musamman kan batun na'urar kere kere.
Akasin haka, kasar Sin ta gabatar da shirinta a bara: tana son ta zama jagora a fannin kirkirar kere kere a shekarar 2030.
"Tun da sauran ƙasashe sun yi nesa da Amurka kuma muna neman ci gaba a fannin kere kere (AI), ninka kasafin kuɗi na AI zai zama kyakkyawan farawa", in ji Lee.
"Tashin hankali na iya ninka damar samun babban nasara a Amurka", in ji Lee a cikin wata hira da CNBC a wannan makon.
Lee, wanda littafinsa mai suna AI Superpowers: China, Silicon Valley and the New World Order, wanda Houghton Mifflin Harcourt ya fitar a wannan makon, shi ne shugaban kamfanin Sinovation Ventures, wanda ya zuba jari a daya daga cikin manyan kamfanonin da ke da alhakin AI a kasar Sin, Face++.
A cikin shekarun 1980s, ya yi aiki a Jami'ar Carnegie Mellon a kan tsarin UI wanda ya doke dan wasan Amurka mafi girma a duniya mai suna Othello, kuma daga baya ya zama babban jami'in Microsoft Research da kuma Shugaba na kamfanin Google na kasar Sin.
Lee ya mayar da martani ga gasar fasahar zamani ta Amurka kamar Robotic Challenge na Hukumar Bincike ta Kariya (Defense Advanced Research Projects Agency) kuma ya tambayi lokacin da za a yi wani wanda zai taimaka wajen gano masu hangen nesa na gaba.
Kamar yadda Lee ya ce, masu bincike a Amirka sukan yi aiki tuƙuru don su samu tallafin gwamnati.
"Ba kasar Sin za ta ba mu shugabannin ilimi ba, amma manyan kamfanoni", in ji Lee.
Facebook, Google da sauran kamfanonin fasaha sun yi amfani da manyan masu fasaha daga jami'o'i a cikin 'yan shekarun nan don su yi musu aikin AI.
Lee ya ce sauye-sauye a manufofin shige da fice na iya taimakawa wajen tallafa wa Amurka a fannin IUD.
"Ina ganin cewa ya kamata a ba da Green Card ga masu samun PhD a fannin AI", in ji shi.
Kwamitin Jiha na kasar Sin ya fitar da shirin bunkasa sabon ƙarni na fasaha a watan Yulin 2017.
Kamfanin kimiyya na kasar Sin na samar da kudade ga masu ilimi a irin yadda National Science Foundation  NSF da sauran hukumomin gwamnati ke ba da kudade ga masana kimiyya na Amurka, amma ingancin aikin kimiyya a kasar Sin ya yi kasa, in ji Lee.
A farkon wannan shekarar, Ma'aikatar Tsaro ta Amurka ta kafa Cibiyar Haɗin Kai na Artificial Intelligence, wadda ke da niyyar haɗa kan masana'antu da masana ilimi.
