Dan wasan mai shekaru 56 yana taka rawar Jack Jarvis a cikin wani shirin BBC wanda ya rubuta kuma ya yi wasa tare da abokin aikinsa na shekaru da yawa, Greg Hemphill.
An sanar da cewa jerin tara masu zuwa za su kasance na ƙarshe, kuma da alama Kiernan yana shirin rayuwa a waje da Glasgow suburb Craiglang (gidan wasan kwaikwayon).
Bisa ga takardun hukuma, shi ne daraktan kamfanin Adriftmorn Limited.
Dan wasan ya ki yin tsokaci kan labarin, amma wata majiya ta ruwaito wa Scottish Sun cewa Kiernan yana son shiga cikin kasuwancin cin abinci mai tasowa a Glasgow.
Teku na Mu: Bolivia, wadda aka yanke daga teku, tana fatan sake samun damar shiga Tekun Fasifik
Masu jirgin ruwa sun kewaye ofishin sojojin ruwa na La Paz suna sanye da riguna.
