LeBron zai fara wasan ne a San Diego ranar Lahadi
Fans da ke jiran wasan farko na LeBron James a Los Angeles Lakers za su yi farin ciki.
Kocin Lakers, Luke Walton, ya sanar da cewa James zai fara wasan farko na gasar a ranar Lahadi da Denver Nuggets a San Diego.
Amma har yanzu ba a yanke shawarar tsawon lokacin da za a yi wasan ba.
"Za a yi fiye da ɗaya kuma ƙasa da 48", in ji Walton a shafin yanar gizon Lakers.
Dan wasan Lakers, Mike Trudell, ya wallafa a shafinsa na Twitter cewa James zai buga wasa na dan lokaci.
Bayan kammala atisayen da aka yi a farkon wannan makon, James ya bayyana shirinsa na buga wasannin farko na Lakers guda shida.
"A wannan lokaci na aikina, ba na bukatar yin gasa don fara wasa", in ji shi.
Taron Trump a West Virginia, tashar YouTube
A yau ne shugaban kasar Amurka Donald Trump ya fara wani taro na neman zabe a birnin Wheeling na jihar West Virginia.
Wannan shi ne na farko daga cikin tarurrukan da Trump zai yi a mako mai zuwa, wanda ya hada da tsayawa a wurare da suka fi kusa da shi, kamar Tennessee da Mississippi.
Bayan an dage zaben wanda zai tsaya a kan kujerar kotun koli, Trump na shirin gina goyon baya ga zaben da za a yi a tsakiyar shekara mai zuwa, domin 'yan Republican na fuskantar asarar iko a zaben na watan Nuwamba.
A wane lokaci ne taron Trump zai gudana a West Virginia, kuma a ina za ku iya kallon taron a kan layi?
Taron Trump a Wheeling, West Virginia, yana gudana a karfe 7:00 na yammacin yammacin yau, Asabar, Satumba 29, 2018.
Za ku iya kallon taron Trump a West Virginia a kan layi a ƙasa, ta hanyar watsa shirye-shirye na YouTube.
Trump na iya yin jawabi game da sauraron da ake yi na dan takarar shugabancin kotun koli, Bret Kavanaugh, wanda ke fuskantar takunkumin cin zarafin mata, yayin da aka dage zaben tabbatar da kujerar majalisa har tsawon mako guda, yayin da ake ci gaba da binciken FBI.
Amma babban manufar wannan jerin tarurruka shi ne, taimaka wa 'yan Republican da ke fuskantar zaɓe mai wuya a watan Nuwamba su sake samun ƙarfi.
A cewar Reuters, taron na biyar na mako mai zuwa, an yi shi ne don karfafa gwiwa da kuma karfafa masu goyon baya, yayin da 'yan Republican ke kokarin karewa da kuma fadada rinjaye da suke da shi a majalisar dattawa da kuma majalisar wakilai.
"Sarrafawa kan majalisa na da matukar muhimmanci ga ajandar shugaban kasa, a lokacin da ya shiga lokacin zaben, shugaban zai ziyarci jihohi da dama", in ji wani mai magana da yawun yakin neman zaben Trump, wanda ya ki bayyana sunansa.
Taron da ake yi a Wesbanco Arena a Wheeling, yana iya jawo hankalin masu goyon baya daga Ohio da Pennsylvania da kuma kafofin watsa labarai daga Pittsburgh, West Virginia Metro News ta ruwaito.
A ranar Asabar, Trump zai ziyarci West Virginia karo na biyu a cikin wata guda, jihar da ya lashe zaben 2016 da kashi 40 cikin dari.
Trump na kokarin tallafawa dan takarar majalisar dattijai na jam'iyyar Republican a West Virginia, Patrick Morrissey, wanda yake kasa a zaben.
"Ba abu mai kyau ba ne ga Morrissey cewa shugaban kasa ya zo ya kara masa fifiko a zaben", in ji Simon Haeder, masanin siyasa a jami'ar West Virginia.
