A ranar wasan karshe na gasar Ryder, Turai ta ci gaba da jagoranci 10-6
Turai za ta shiga ranar karshe ta gasar Ryder Cup da gagarumar nasara bayan kammala wasannin hudu da hudu a ranar Asabar da ta yi wa Amurka nasara da maki goma da shida.
Tommy Fleetwood da Francesco Molinari sun jagoranci harin ne da nasara biyu a kan Tiger Woods mai wahala, don samun maki huɗu a Le Golf National.
Ƙungiyar Turai ta Thomas Bjorn, a ƙoƙarin riƙe da kofin da suka rasa a Hazeltine shekaru biyu da suka gabata, sun mamaye ƙungiyar Amurka da ta gaza a wasannin kwallon kafa na safe, kuma sun ci wasan 3-1.
A wasan hudu, Amurkawa sun fi tsayayya, sun ci biyu, amma ba su iya rufe matsalar su ba.
Jam'iyyar Jim Furyke na bukatar maki takwas daga wasanni 12 na 'yan wasa a ranar Lahadi domin ta ci gaba da rike kofin.
Fleetwood shine dan wasan Turai na farko da ya ci maki hudu a jere, yayin da shi da Molinari, wanda ake kira "Molliwood", bayan karshen mako mai ban mamaki, su ne kawai biyu da suka ci maki hudu a wasanninsu na farko a tarihin Ryder Cup.
Bayan sun doke Woods da Patrick Reed a wasan kwallon kwando, sun kara da cewa sun doke Woods da dan wasan Amurka na farko, Bryson Dechambeau, da ci 5 da 4.
Woods, wanda ya yi wasa biyu a ranar Asabar, ya nuna wasu 'yan wasan da suka yi fice, amma a ƙarshe ya rasa 19 daga cikin wasansa 29 na wasan kwallon kafa da na hudu da kuma bakwai a jere.
Justin Rose, wanda ya yi watsi da wasannin kwallon kafa na safe, ya dawo ya raka Henrik Stenson a wasan hudu, tare da doke Dustin Johnson da Brooks Koepka 2&1  na daya da uku a cikin jerin duniya.
Amma, a wannan rana mai kyau da ke kudu maso yammacin Paris, Turai ba ta da sauƙi.
