Alfredo Morelos ya yi ikirarin cin kwallo bayan minti 15 da buga wasan lokacin da ya yi karo da Steven Lawless, amma mai wasan kwaikwayo Steven Thomson ya ki amincewa da bukatar dan wasan Colombia.
Rangers sun yi harbi biyu a raga a farkon rabin wasan, amma tsohon mai tsaron gidan Ibrox, Liam Kelly, ya yi kasa da kasa da ciwon kai na Lassan Coulibaly da kuma wani ɗan ƙaramin harbi na Ovie Eyar.
Ko da yake kwallo na farko da Livi ya ci a minti na 34 zai iya kawo cikas a wasan, babu wanda zai ce sun cancanci hakan domin sun yi kokari sosai.
Rangers sun sake kasawa da Jacobs Horn.
Scott Arfield bai amsa ba lokacin da Declan Gallagher ya tura kwallon a kan Scott Robinson, wanda ya riƙe kansa a hankali kuma ya zaɓi Mengu don sauƙi.
Gerrard ya yi aiki a lokacin hutu, ya maye gurbin Coulibaly da Ryan Kent kuma musayar ta kasance kusan nan take lokacin da mai tsaron gida ya sami Morelos, amma Kelly mai ban sha'awa ya yi hanzarin fita daga layinsa kuma ya toshe shi.
Amma Livingston ya ci gaba da tilasta wa baƙi su yi irin wasan da suke so, yayin da Lithgow da Halkett suka yi harbi mai tsawo.
Holt ya iya karawa da shi a wasan karshe, amma McGregor ya kare Jacobs da kyau, sannan ya tsayayya da Lithgow a kan kusurwa.
Mai maye gurbin Rangers, Glenn Middleton, ya sake yin ikirarin fanareti bayan ya shiga tsakani da Jacobs, amma Thomson ya sake yin watsi da hakan.
Tarihi: Wanda Ya kirkiro kwamfutar Geiger
Kuma yanzu ga wani shafi daga jaridarmu ta safe ta ranar Lahadi: Satumba 30, 1882, shekaru 136 da suka wuce... wannan shine ranar da aka haifi masanin kimiyyar lissafi na gaba a Jamus, Johannes Wilhelm "Hans" Geiger.
Geiger ya kirkiro wata hanya ta gano da kuma auna radiyo, abin da ya kai ga gina na'urar da ake kira kwamfutar Geiger.
Kwamfuta ta Geiger, ban da kasancewa cikin fannin kimiyya har yau, ta zama babban al'adun al'adu lokacin da aka yi magana game da ita a fim din 1950 "Bells of Coronado" da cowboys masu goyon bayan kimiyya Roy Rogers da Dale Evans suka yi:
Mutum: "Mece ce wannan?"
Rogers: Wannan kwamfutar Geiger ce, tana gano ma'adanai masu hasken wuta, kamar uranium.
Idan ka saka belun kunne, za ka ji ainihin sauti na atoms da ke haifar da rediyo a cikin ma'adanai.
Evans: "Na yi imani, na ji suna fashewa!"
Hans Geiger ya mutu a shekara ta 1945, 'yan kwanaki kafin ya cika shekara 63.
