HIV/Aids: Kasar Sin ta ba da rahoton karuwar sabbin kamuwa da cutar da kashi 14%
Kasar Sin ta samu karuwar mutane 14 cikin 100 da ke rayuwa da cutar HIV da kuma AIDS.
Jami'an kiwon lafiya sun ce mutane sama da 820,000 ne ke da cutar a kasar.
A cikin kwata na biyu na 2018 kadai, an samu sabbin mutane sama da 40 000.
Yawancin sababbin cututtuka sun kasance masu yaduwa ta hanyar jima'i, wanda shine canji daga baya.
A al'adance, cutar HIV ta yadu cikin sauri a wasu sassan kasar Sin ta hanyar kamuwa da jini.
Amma adadin mutanen da suka kamu da cutar HIV ta wannan hanyar ya ragu zuwa kusan babu, in ji jami'an kiwon lafiya na kasar Sin a wani taro a lardin Yunnan.
Amma a shekara guda, adadin mutanen da ke da cutar HIV da AIDS a China ya ƙaru da mutane 100,000.
Cutar HIV ta hanyar jima'i na da matukar damuwa a cikin al'ummar LGBT na kasar Sin.
An yi wa luwadi yancin yin jima'i a kasar Sin a shekarar 1997, amma nuna bambanci ga mutanen LGBT har yanzu ya zama ruwan dare.
Saboda ra'ayin da ya dace da ƙasashe, binciken ya kiyasta cewa kashi 70  90 cikin ɗari na maza da suka yi jima'i da maza za su yi aure da mata.
Yawancin cututtukan da ake yadawa sun samo asali ne daga rashin kariya ta jima'i a cikin waɗannan alaƙar.
Tun daga shekara ta 2003, gwamnatin kasar Sin ta yi alkawarin samar da maganin cutar HIV ga kowa a matsayin wani ɓangare na ƙoƙarin magance matsalar.
Maxine Waters ta musanta cewa wani ma'aikaciyarta ta ba da bayanan 'yan majalisar dattijai na GOP, ta soki "karya mai haɗari" da "ka'idar makirci"
A ranar Asabar, 'yar majalisar wakilai ta Amurka Maxine Waters ta musanta zargin cewa wani ma'aikaciyarta ya tura bayanan sirri na 'yan majalisar dattijai uku na Republican zuwa shafin Wikipedia na 'yan majalisar.
'Yar Democrat a Los Angeles ta ce zargin ya fito ne daga wasu shafukan yanar gizo da kuma masana masu ra'ayin nuna bambanci.
"Ƙarya, ƙarya da sauran ƙazantar ƙarya", in ji Waters a cikin wata sanarwa a shafin Twitter.
An ce bayanan da aka fitar sun ƙunshi adireshin gida da kuma lambobin waya na 'yan majalisar dattawa Lindsey Graham na South Carolina da Mike Lee da Orrin Hatch, duka biyu 'yan Utah.
Bayanan sun bayyana a shafin yanar gizo a ranar Alhamis, wanda wani mutum da ba a san shi ba ya wallafa su a Capitol Hill a lokacin da aka yi wa 'yan majalisar dattawa shari'ar cin zarafin dan takarar kotun koli Brett Kavanaugh.
Bayanin ya fita ne bayan wasu 'yan majalisar dattawa uku sun yi wa Kavanaugh tambayoyi.
Shafukan yanar gizo masu ra'ayin mazan jiya kamar su Gateway Pundit da RedState sun sanar da cewa adiresoshin IP da ke gano tushen ɓarnar suna da alaƙa da ofishin Waters kuma sun ba da bayanin wani memba na ma'aikatan Waters, Hill ya ruwaito.
"Wannan zargi da ba a tabbatar da shi ba gaskiya ne kuma karya ne", Waters ta ci gaba.
Majalisarmu da aka yi wa karya a cikin wannan ƙarar ta hanyar yaudara da kuma ƙarya, ba ta da alhakin ɓarnatar da wannan bayanin.
Wannan zargin da ba a tabbatar da shi ba, ba gaskiya ba ne kuma ba gaskiya ba ne.
Sanarwar Waters ta jawo suka kan layi, ciki har da wasu daga tsohon sakataren yada labarai na fadar White House, Ari Fleischer.
"Rashin yarda da ita cike take da fushi", in ji Fleischer.
Wannan yana nuna cewa ba ta da halin da ya dace ta zama 'yar majalisa.
Idan aka zargi mutum da abin da bai yi ba, kada ka yi fushi.
Kada ya yi tawaye.
Bai kamata ya ƙalubalanci dalilin da ya sa mai gabatar da kara yake yin wannan shari'a ba.
Dole ne ya kasance mai natsuwa da daidaitacce.
Fleischer ya yi kwatancen yadda Waters ya amsa sukar da aka yi wa mai shari'a Kavanaugh daga 'yan Democrat, wanda suka zarge shi da yin fushi sosai a lokacin sauraron shari'ar ranar Alhamis.
Omar Navarro, dan takarar Republican da ke neman kujerar Waters a zaben fidda gwani, shi ma ya bayyana ra'ayinsa a shafin Twitter.
"Idan gaskiya ne, to babban abu ne", in ji shi.
A cikin sanarwar da ta bayar, Waters ta ce ofishinta ya sanar da hukumomin da ke da alhakin shari'a game da zargin yaudara.
"Za mu tabbatar da cewa an gano masu laifin", ta ci gaba, "kuma za su dauki alhakin ayyukansu, wanda ke da lahani da kuma hadari ga dukkan ma'aikatan na".
Johnny English ya sake shiga cikin fim din
A yau, abu ne na yau da kullum a ga duk wani sabon fim da ke da ra'ayi na Birtaniya yana da alaƙa da Brexit, kuma wannan ya shafi wannan sake haifuwa na wani wasan kwaikwayo na wasan kwaikwayo na Johnny English  wanda aka fara a 2003 tare da Johnny English kuma ya sake dawowa cikin 2011 tare da Johnny English ya dawo.
Za a yi wa kanmu ba'a game da yadda muka kasa samun sabon kayan fitarwa na kasa?
Ko ta yaya, Johnny English da ba shi da ƙwarewa da kuma fuskarsa ta musamman ya sami damar sake ɓata komai  tare da sunansa yana nuna alama fiye da komai cewa shi mai karimci ne mai ban dariya wanda aka tsara musamman don masu sauraro ba Ingilishi ba.
Shi ne, ba shakka, wannan ɗan ɓoye mai ɓoye wanda, duk da cewa yana da ɗan ƙaramin sha'awa, yana da ɗan Clouseau, ɗan ɗan Mr Bean, da kuma ɗan ɗan ɗan ɗan mutumin da ya ba da sautin waƙa guda ɗaya na waƙar "Chariots of Fire" a bikin buɗe gasar Olympics ta London ta 2012.
Halinsa na asali ya samo asali ne daga matafiyi na duniya da kuma wani mutum mai ban mamaki wanda Atkinson ya taɓa yin sa a cikin tallan TV da aka manta da su a yau don Barclaycard, yana barin rikici a ko'ina.
A cikin wannan sabon abu na Johnny English, za a iya samun wani abu mai kyau ko biyu.
Ina son yadda Johnny English ya zo wurin jirgin sama mai saukar ungulu sanye da makamai na dā kuma jirgin ya yi karo da kwalkwali.
Wannan ya nuna baiwar Atkinson na yin wasan kwaikwayo, amma wasan kwaikwayo yana da ɗan ƙaramin ƙarfi kuma yana da ban mamaki, musamman ma lokacin da manyan fina-finai kamar 007 da Mission Impossible kansu a yau suna ba da wasan kwaikwayo a matsayin ɗaya daga cikin abubuwan da suke ciki.
Abin dariya kamar yana nufin yara ne fiye da manya, kuma a wurina ba irin abubuwan ban mamaki da Johnny English ya yi ba ne kamar yadda Atkinson ya yi ba tare da ya faɗi ba game da Mr. Bean.
Ainihin abin da fim ɗin yake nufi shi ne cewa ƙasar Ingila tana cikin matsala.
Wani dan gwanin kwamfuta ya shiga cikin wani shafin yanar gizo na 'yan leken asiri na Birtaniya, kuma ya tsoratar da mai ba da shawara Kevin Eldon, wanda ya yi kasa da wasa, ya gano ainihin duk jami'an Birtaniya a yankin.
Wannan shi ne na karshe ga Firayim Minista, wanda yake da ban mamaki da kuma fadace-fadace, wanda ya riga ya kasance a kan gefen rushewa saboda rashin sha'awar siyasa: Emma Thompson yana yin abin da ta iya tare da wani abu mai kama da Theresa May, amma ba shi da yawa a cikin rubutun.
Masu ba ta shawara a kan harkokin yawon bude ido sun gaya mata cewa idan aka gano duk wani ɗan leƙen asiri da ke aiki a ƙasar, za ta bukaci a yi wa wani murabus.
Sai Johnny English ya zo, wanda a yau shi ne darektan wani babban jami'i, yana koyar da darussa na sirri na yadda za a zama ɗan leƙen asiri: akwai wasu abubuwa masu ban sha'awa kamar yadda English yake koyar da darussan leƙen asiri a cikin hanyar Rock School.
Don haka aka sake kiran Inglish zuwa Whitehall don sanarwar gaggawa kuma ya haɗu da tsohon mai ba da shawara na dogon lokaci Bough, wanda Ben Miller ya sake buga shi.
Bough yanzu ya yi aure, yana da dangantaka da wani kwamandan jirgin ruwa mai cike da damuwa, wanda Vicki Pepperdine ke taka rawa.
Sai Batman da Robin, manyan masu kawo bala'i a cikin ayyukan sirrin Sarauniya, suka dawo cikin filin wasa, suka haɗu da kyakkyawar femme fatale, Ophelia Bullet, kamar yadda Olga Kurylenko ta gabatar.
A halin yanzu, Firayim Minista ta shiga cikin wani yanayi mai haɗari na mai karɓar kuɗi na fasaha wanda ke da'awar cewa zai iya magance matsalolin kwamfuta na Burtaniya: Jason Walt mai ban tsoro wanda Jake Lacy ya buga.
Turanci da Bough sun fara odyssey na rikice-rikice masu ban dariya: suna sanya gidan cin abinci na Faransa mai haske a cikin tufafin masu jiran aiki; suna haifar da rikici lokacin da suka shiga cikin jirgin ruwan Volt; kuma Turanci ya haifar da rashin tsari mai tsabta lokacin da ya yi ƙoƙarin amfani da na'urar gaskiya ta gaskiya don sanin abubuwan da ke cikin gidan Volt.
Dukkanin abubuwan da ake yi suna fitowa daga hannunsu a minti na ƙarshe, amma duk da cewa suna da ban sha'awa da kuma tashin hankali, duk abin da ke faruwa yana kama da shirin talabijin na yara.
Dukkanin ra'ayi na matsakaici ne.
Kamar yadda yake a sauran fina-finai da Johnny English ya yi, ina tunanin me ya sa masana'antar fim ta Burtaniya ba za ta ba Rowan Atkinson rawar da ta dace da baiwa ba?
'Yan Labour sun ki amincewa da aikin da aka tsara na Birtaniya na aikin kwana hudu da ake biya a matsayin kwana biyar
An ce jam'iyyar Jeremy Corbyn ta Labour ta yi la'akari da wani tsari na musamman wanda zai bai wa 'yan Birtaniya aiki na kwana hudu amma a biya su albashi na kwana biyar.
An ce jam'iyyar tana son shugabannin kamfanoni su raba kuɗin da aka samu daga juyin juya halin kere kere (AI) ta hanyar ba ma'aikata karin ranar hutu.
Hakan zai sa ma'aikatan su yi hutu na kwana uku a mako, amma su riƙa biyan su daidai da na dā.
Majiyoyin sun ce wannan ra'ayin ya yi daidai da shirin tattalin arzikin jam'iyyar na karkatar da kasar ga ma'aikata.
An amince da sauyawar zuwa mako guda hudu a taron ma'aikata na kasa da kasa a matsayin hanyar da ma'aikata za su iya cin gajiyar canjin tattalin arziki.
Wani babban jami'in jam'iyyar Labour ya shaida wa The Sunday Times cewa: "Muna sa ran za a fitar da wannan bita a karshen shekara.
Ba za a yi ba daga dare zuwa safe, amma aikin kwana huɗu wani ƙoƙari ne da ya dace da tsarin jam'iyyar na daidaita tattalin arziki don amfanin ma'aikata da kuma tsarin dabarun masana'antar jam'iyyar gaba ɗaya.
Jam'iyyar Green Party ta saka wa'adin aiki na kwana hudu a cikin kamfen din ta na zaben 2017.
Amma har yanzu, jam'iyyar Labour ba ta yi nasara ba.
Mai magana da yawun jam'iyyar Labour ya ce: "Aikin kwana hudu ba siyasa ba ce, kuma ba a yin la'akari da ita".
Shadow Chancellor John McDonnell ya yi amfani da taron Labour na makon da ya gabata don gabatar da hangen nesan sa na juyin juya halin zamantakewar al'umma a tattalin arziki.
Mista McDonnell ya bayyana aniyarsa ta dawo da iko daga "anonymous" da "masu arziki" a bangaren ayyuka.
Shadow Chancellor din na shirin cewa masu hannun jari na yanzu a kamfanonin ruwa ba za su dawo da dukkan hannun jarin su ba, saboda gwamnatin Labour na iya amfani da "cuts" saboda laifin da aka gano.
Ya kuma tabbatar da tsare-tsaren sanya ma'aikata a cikin hukumomin kamfanoni da kuma kafa Asusun Mallaka na Musamman don samun kashi 10 cikin 100 na kadarorin kamfanoni a cikin kamfanoni masu zaman kansu ga ma'aikata, wanda hakan zai iya ba su ribar shekara-shekara har zuwa £500.
Lindsey Graham da John Kennedy sun yi magana a shirin 60 Minutes cewa binciken da FBI ke yi game da Kavanaugh zai iya canja ra'ayinsu
Binciken da hukumar ta FBI ke yi kan zargin da ake yi wa mai shari'a Brett Kavanaugh ya jinkirta kada kuri'ar zabensa a kotun koli na kasar nan da akalla mako guda, kuma ya yi tambaya ko binciken hukumar zai iya rinjayar wasu 'yan majalisar dattijai na Republican su janye goyon bayansu.
A wata hira da aka yi da 'yan jaridar 60 Minutes, Scott Pelley, ya tambayi 'yan majalisar wakilai John Kennedy da Lindsey Graham, ko akwai wani abu da hukumar ta FBI za ta iya gano da zai sa su canja ra'ayinsu.
Kennedy ya fi abokinsa na South Carolina nuna cewa yana da gaskiya.
"Amma ba shakka", in ji Kennedy.
Kamar yadda na ce, lokacin da na je wurin shari'a, na yi magana da Alkalin Kavanaugh.
Na kira shi lokacin da ya faru, lokacin da aka gabatar da tuhuma, na tambaye shi, "Shin kun yi hakan?"
Ya kasance mai ƙuduri, mai ƙuduri da kuma mai ba da shawara.
Amma, kamar dai Graham ya riga ya tsai da shawara.
"Na riga na yanke shawara game da Brett Kavanaugh, kuma dole ne a kawo wani zargi mai tsanani", in ji shi.
"Dr Ford, ban san abin da ya faru ba, amma na san wannan: Brett ya musanta hakan", Graham ya kara da cewa, yana mai ambaton Christine Blasey Ford.
Kuma babu wanda ya ambata da zai iya tabbatar da hakan.
Wannan abu yana da shekaru 36.
Ba na ganin yadda za a canja kome.
Menene bikin Global Citizen kuma yana taimakawa wajen rage talauci?
A ranar Asabar, za a yi bikin Global Citizen a birnin New York, wani biki na shekara-shekara da ake yi a inda taurari masu yawa suke nuna burinsu na kawo ƙarshen yunwa a duniya.
A shekara ta bakwai, dubban mutane za su taru a babban filin shakatawa na Central Park, ba wai kawai don su ji daɗin masu fasaha kamar Janet Jackson, Cardi B, da Shawn Mendes ba, amma kuma don su kara wayar da kan jama'a game da ainihin manufar taron, wato kawar da matsanancin talauci a shekara ta 2030.
Bikin Global Citizen, wanda aka fara gudanarwa a shekarar 2012, wani bangare ne na Global Poverty Project, wata kungiya ta kasa da kasa da ke neman kawo karshen talauci ta hanyar kara yawan mutanen da ke yaki da talauci.
Idan masu kallo suna son samun tikiti na kyauta (sai dai idan suna son biyan tikitin VIP), dole ne su cika jerin ayyuka, ko ayyuka, kamar aikin sa kai, aika imel zuwa ga shugaban duniya, kiran waya, ko wata hanya mai ma'ana don fadakar da jama'a game da manufar taron, wato kawar da talauci.
Shekaru 12 sun rage, to, shin Global Citizen tana iya cimma burinta?
Shin ra'ayin bayar da kyauta ga mutane ta hanyar yin wasa kyauta hanya ce mai kyau ta shawo kan mutane su nemi a yi aiki ko kuwa wani abu ne da ake kira "clicktivism" inda mutane ke jin cewa suna kawo canji ta hanyar sanya hannu kan takarda ta yanar gizo ko kuma yin tweet?
Kungiyar Global Citizen ta ce sun samu sama da rabon mutane miliyan 19 daga masu goyon bayansu tun daga shekarar 2011, suna ci gaba da yin wasu abubuwa.
Ƙungiyar ta ce waɗannan abubuwan sun taimaka wajen sa shugabannin duniya su ba da alkawari da kuma manufofi masu daraja fiye da dala biliyan 37 da za su shafi rayukan mutane biliyan 2.25 a shekara ta 2030.
A farkon 2018, kungiyar ta ce hannun jarin ta ya samar da alkawura da sanarwa 390, inda a kalla dala biliyan 10 aka biya ko aka tara.
Ƙungiyar ta kimanta cewa, kusan mutane miliyan 649 a dukan duniya sun sami amfanin tanadin da aka yi musu a kai a kai.
Misalin alkawuran sun hada da The Power of Nutrition, wata kungiya ta masu zuba jari da masu samar da kayayyaki dake Birnin Birtaniya, wadanda suka yi alkawarin "taimakawa yara su samu cikakkiyar damar su", tare da alkawarin bayar da dala miliyan 35 ga kasar Rwanda domin taimakawa wajen kawo karshen rashin abinci mai gina jiki a kasar bayan sun samu tweets sama da 4,700 daga Global Citizens.
"Tare da goyon bayan gwamnatin Burtaniya, masu bayar da tallafi, gwamnatocin kasa da kuma 'yan kasa na duniya kamar ku, za mu iya kawo rashin abinci mai gina jiki a baya", in ji Tracey Ullman, jakadan The Power of Nutrition, a wani taron jama'a a London a watan Afrilu na 2018.
Ƙungiyar ta kuma ce bayan da aka yi fiye da 5,000 na kira ga inganta abinci mai gina jiki ga mata da yara a Burtaniya, gwamnati ta sanar da bayar da tallafin The Power of Nuttion, wanda zai samar da tallafin abinci ga mata da yara miliyan 5.
A amsa ga wata tambaya da ake yawan yi a shafin yanar gizon, "A kan me kuke ganin za mu iya kawo ƙarshen matsanancin talauci?"
Global Citizen ta amsa: "Za mu yi tafiya mai tsawo da wahala, wani lokaci za mu fadi kuma mu kasa.
Amma kamar manyan ƙungiyoyin 'yancin jama'a da na nuna wariyar launin fata da suka riga suka shige, za mu yi nasara domin tare muna da ƙarfi.
Janet Jackson, Weeknd, Shawn Mendes, Cardi B, Janelle Monae suna cikin mutanen da za su yi magana a taron na wannan shekara a New York, tare da masu gabatar da Deborah-Lee Furness da Hugh Jackman.
Amurka na iya amfani da rundunar sojin ruwa a matsayin "ta'asa" don takaita fitar da makamashin Rasha, in ji sakataren cikin gida.
"Idan ya zama dole, Washington na iya kiran rundunar sojin ruwanta don hana shigowar makamashin Rasha zuwa kasuwannin da suka hada da Gabas ta Tsakiya, "in ji Sakataren Harkokin Cikin Gida na Amurka Ryan Zinke, kamar yadda Washington Examiner ta ruwaito shi.
Zinke ya ce, shigar Rasha cikin Syria  inda suke aiki bisa gayyatar gwamnatin halal  wata hujja ce ta gano sabbin kasuwannin makamashi.
"Ina ganin babban dalilin da ya sa suke Gabas ta Tsakiya shi ne domin suna son su yi kasuwanci da makamashi a can kamar yadda suke yi a gabashin Turai, kudancin Turai", in ji shi.
Ya ce akwai hanyoyi da hanyoyin da za a bi don magance wannan.
"Amurka za ta iya amfani da rundunar sojin ruwa wajen tabbatar da cewa hanyoyin ruwa sun kasance a bude, kuma idan ya zama dole, ta yi toshe-tashen hankula don tabbatar da cewa ba a sayar da makamashinta ba", in ji shi.
Zinke ya yi magana ne ga masu halarta a wani taron da ake gudanarwa a karkashin jagorancin Ƙungiyar Masu Amfani da Makamashi, wata ƙungiya mai zaman kanta da ke neman zama "Muryar Masu Amfani da Makamashi" a Amurka.
Ya kuma kwatanta yadda Washington ke bi da Rasha da Iran, inda ya ce sun yi daidai.
"Hanyar tattalin arziki da za a iya bi da Iran da Rasha ita ce ta rage amfani da man fetur", in ji shi, inda ya ce Rasha tana da wata dabara guda daya a aljihunta, domin tattalin arzikinta ya dogara ne da man fetur.
Wannan furucin ya zo ne a daidai lokacin da gwamnatin Trump ta fara aikin da ta ke yi na tallafawa fitar da iskar gas mai narkewa zuwa Turai da kuma maye gurbin Rasha, wanda ya fi sauki ga masu amfani da Turai.
Don haka, jami'an gwamnatin Trump, ciki har da shugaban Amurka Donald Trump, suna kokarin shawo kan Jamus ta janye daga aikin "Nord Stream 2", wanda Trump ya ce zai sa Berlin ta zama fursuna ga Moscow.
Moscow ta sha jaddada cewa, aikin da ake kira Nord Stream 2 mai darajar dala biliyan 11, wanda ake sa ran zai ninka karfin da ake da shi na aikin zuwa miliyan biliyan 110, aikin tattalin arziki ne.
Kremlin ya ce hamayya da Washington ke yi da aikin na da manufa ce ta tattalin arziki kuma misali ne na rashin adalci.
"Na tabbata muna da ra'ayi guda cewa ba za a iya amfani da makamashi a matsayin kayan aiki na turawa ba kuma ya kamata masu amfani su sami damar zaɓar masu samar da su", in ji Ministan Makamashi na Rasha Aleksandr Novak bayan ganawa da Sakataren Makamashi na Amurka Rick Perry a Moscow a watan Satumba.
Matsayin Amurka ya jawo adawa daga Jamus, wanda ya tabbatar da jajircewarsa ga aikin.
Babban kungiyar masana'antu ta Jamus, BDI, ta bukaci Amurka da ta guji shiga cikin manufofin makamashi na EU da yarjejeniyar biyu tsakanin Berlin da Moscow.
"Ina da babbar matsala da wata kasa ta uku da ke tsoma baki a samar da makamashi", in ji Dieter Kempf, daraktan kungiyar masana'antun Jamus (BDI), bayan ganawar da aka yi kwanan nan tsakanin shugabar gwamnatin Jamus Angela Merkel da shugaban Rasha Vladimir Putin.
Elizabeth Warren za ta yi la'akari sosai da neman takarar shugaban kasa a 2020, in ji Sanata daga Massachusetts
Sanata Elizabeth Warren ta Massachusetts ta ce a ranar Asabar za ta yi la'akari da takarar shugaban kasa bayan zaben fidda gwani.
A taron da aka yi a fadar garin Holyoke, Massachusetts, Warren ta tabbatar da cewa za ta yi la'akari da takarar.
"Lokaci ya yi da mata za su je Washington don gyara gwamnatinmu da ta lalace, kuma hakan na bukatar mace a matsayin shugaban kasa", in ji ta, a cewar The Hill.
"Bayan 6 ga Nuwamba, zan yi tunani sosai game da neman takarar shugaban kasa".
Warren ta yi magana a kan shugaban kasa Donald Trump a lokacin taron majalisar cewa tana kai kasar nan ga hanyar da ba ta dace ba.
"Ina matukar fargabar abin da Donald Trump ke yi wa dimokiradiyya", in ji ta.
Warren ta yi ta sukar Trump da kuma wanda ya tsaya takara a kotun koli, Brett Kavanaugh.
A ranar Juma'a ta wallafa a shafin Twitter cewa, "Tabbas muna bukatar binciken FBI kafin a kada kuri'ar".
Amma kuri'ar da aka fitar a ranar Alhamis ta nuna cewa mafi yawan masu jefa kuri'ar Warren ba su yi imanin cewa ya kamata ta tsaya takara a shekarar 2020 ba.
Wani bincike da aka yi a Cibiyar Bincike a Siyasa ta Jami'ar Suffolk/Boston Globe ya nuna cewa kashi hamsin cikin dari na masu jefa kuri'a a Massachusetts sun ce bai kamata a zabi 'yar majalisar dattijai ba.
Kashi talatin da biyu cikin dari za su goyi bayan takarar ta.
