Sarah Palin tana magana a taron Donald Trump game da PTSD
Track Palin, mai shekara 26, an tura shi zuwa rundunar soja a ranar 11 ga Satumba, 2007, kuma ya yi shekara guda a Iraki.
A ranar Litinin da yamma aka kama shi kuma aka tuhume shi da cin zarafin cikin gida.
"A cikin abin da ɗana ya shiga tun dawowarsa, na iya ji kamar sauran iyalai da ke fama da sakamakon PTSD da raunin da sojojinmu suka dawo da shi", in ji ta ga masu sauraro a taron Donald Trump a Tulsa, Oklahoma.
Palin ta kira kama shi "giwa a cikin dakin" kuma ta ce game da ɗanta da sauran tsoffin sojin, "suna dawowa gida da wasu, masu tsananin gaske, suna dawowa da tambayar ko mutane suna da girmamawa ga abin da 'yan uwan su da matukan jirgi da sauran membobin sojoji suka ba wa wannan ƙasar".
