Jakadan Amurka ya zargi China da cin zarafin mutane ta hanyar tallar farfaganda
Mako guda bayan da jaridar kasar Sin ta wallafa wani talla mai shafi hudu a wata jaridar Amurka da ke tallata amfanin kasuwanci tsakanin Amurka da China, jakadan Amurka ya zargi China da amfani da jaridar Amurka wajen yada farfaganda.
Shugaban Amurka Donald Trump ya yi nuni da wani talla da aka biya na jaridar China Daily a cikin jaridar Des Moines Register, jaridar Iowa mafi sayarwa, a ranar Laraba bayan ya zargi China da son shiga cikin zaben 'yan majalisar dattijai na Amurka da za a gudanar a ranar 6 ga watan Nuwamba, amma China ta musanta zargin.
A cewar jami'an Amurka ga kamfanin dillancin labarai na Reuters, zargin da Trump ya yi wa Beijing na kokarin tsoma baki a zaben Amurka wani sabon mataki ne a cikin wani yunkuri na kara matsa lamba kan China.
Ko da yake yana da kyau gwamnatoci na ƙasashen waje su yi tallace-tallace don su tallafa wa kasuwanci, Beijing da Washington suna faɗa cikin yaƙin kasuwanci da ke ƙaruwa, inda suke daidaita haraji a kan kayayyakin da suke shigowa da su.
A farkon rikicin cinikayya, takunkumin da China ta yi a baya ya kamata ya shafi masu fitar da kayayyaki a jihohi kamar Iowa, wadanda ke goyon bayan jam'iyyar Republican ta Trump, in ji masana na China da na Amurka.
Terry Branstad, jakadan Amurka a China kuma tsohon gwamnan Iowa, babban mai fitar da kayayyakin gona zuwa China, ya ce Beijing ta cutar da ma'aikatan Amurka, manoma da kamfanoni.
Kamar yadda Branstad ya rubuta a cikin rubutun da ya rubuta a cikin jaridar Des Moines Register ta ranar Lahadi, "China ta ninka ta'addanci ta hanyar buga tallan talla a cikin jaridarmu mai 'yanci".
"Ta hanyar yada farfagandar ta, China tana amfani da al'adun Amurka na 'yancin magana da 'yancin latsawa ta hanyar buga tallace-tallace da aka biya a cikin Des Moines Register", in ji Branstad.
"A akasin haka, a rumfar jarida a kan tituna a nan Beijing, za ku ga 'yan murya kaɗan ne kawai da suka ƙi kuma ba za ku ga ainihin hoton ra'ayoyi daban-daban da 'yan kasar Sin za su iya yi game da matsalar tattalin arzikin China ba, saboda kafofin watsa labarai suna ƙarƙashin ikon jam'iyyar kwaminis ta kasar Sin", in ji shi.
Ya kara da cewa wasu manyan jaridun kasar Sin sun ki amincewa da shi wajen buga labarin, duk da cewa bai bayyana ko wane ne ba.
Masu sharhi sun ce saboda matsalar Kavanaugh, 'yan Republican za su yi nasara a zaben mata.
Da yake manyan 'yan Republican suna goyon bayan da kuma kare dan takarar kotun koli, Brett Kavanaugh, wanda ke fuskantar tuhume-tuhume da dama na cin zarafin mata, manazarta sun yi gargadin cewa hakan zai jawo musu azaba a zaben da ke tafe, musamman daga mata.
Tashin hankali da ke tattare da wannan shari'ar ya kasance mai ƙarfi sosai kuma yawancin 'yan Republican sun riga sun bayyana cewa suna son shiga cikin jefa kuri'a.
"Ba za a iya dawo da waɗannan abubuwa ba", in ji Grant Reeher, farfesa a fannin siyasa a Makarantar Maxwell ta Jami'ar Syracuse, a wata kasida da aka wallafa a The Hill a ranar Asabar.
Reeher ya ce yana shakkar cewa bukatar da Sanata Jeff Flake (R-Arizona) ya yi na neman a yi bincike a FBI a lokacin karshe zai isa ya kwantar da hankalin masu jefa kuri'a.
Mata ba za su manta da abin da ya faru jiya ba, ba za su manta da shi ba gobe ko a watan Nuwamba, "in ji Karine Jean-Pierr, mai ba da shawara da kuma mai magana da yawun kungiyar masu ci gaba ta MoveOn, ga jaridar Washington a ranar Juma'a.
A safiyar Juma'a masu zanga-zanga sun yi ihu a cikin zauren majalisar dattawa "Nuwamba ta kusa!" yayin da 'yan Republican na kwamitin shari'a suka yanke shawarar ci gaba da takarar Kavanaugh duk da shaidar Dr. Christine Blasey Ford, in ji Mic.
"Himma da himma na dimokiradiyya sun wuce iyaka", in ji Stu Rothenberg, wani mai sharhi kan siyasa.
Mutane suna cewa dalili ya yi yawa a yanzu; kuma gaskiya ne.
Amma za ta iya zama mafi girma, musamman tsakanin mata masu jefa kuri'a a cikin birane da kuma matasa masu jefa kuri'a masu shekaru 18 zuwa 29, waɗanda ba sa son shugaban ƙasa amma ba sa yawan jefa kuri'a.
Tun kafin Ford ta ba da shaida a fili inda ta bayyana dalla-dalla zargin da ta yi wa dan takarar kotun koli, manazarta sun nuna cewa za a iya samun gagarumar amsa idan 'yan Republican suka tabbatar da goyon bayansu.
"Game da jam'iyyar GOP, wannan ya zama babban rikici", in ji Michael Steele, tsohon shugaban kwamitin Republican National Committee, a farkon makon da ya gabata, a cewar NBC News.
"Ba wai kawai batun zaben kwamitin ba ne ko kuma na karshe ko kuma ko Kavanaugh zai hau kujerar shugaban kasa, amma kuma yadda 'yan Republican suka dauki lamarin da kuma yadda suka yi da shi", in ji Guy Cecil, daraktan kungiyar Priorities USA, wadda ke taimakawa wajen zaben 'yan Democrat.
Amma dai, jama'ar Amirka sun rabu a kan wanda za su yarda da shi a kan shaidar Ford da Kavanaugh, inda suka fi amincewa da Ford.
Wani sabon bincike da aka yi daga YouGov ya nuna cewa kashi 41 cikin 100 na masu amsa sun tabbata ko kuma sun yi imani da shaidar Ford, yayin da kashi 35 cikin 100 suka ce sun tabbata ko kuma sun yi imani da Kavanaugh.
Bugu da ƙari, kashi 38 cikin ɗari sun ce suna ganin Kavanaugh ya yi ƙarya ko kuma ya yi ƙarya a lokacin da yake ba da shaida, yayin da kashi 30 cikin ɗari suka ce haka ne game da Ford.
Bayan da Flake ya kore shi, FBI tana binciken zargin da Ford ta yi, da kuma akalla mai shigar da kara guda, Deborah Ramirez, in ji jaridar The Guardian.
Ford ta shaida wa kwamitin shari'a na majalisar dattawa a makon da ya gabata cewa Kavanaugh ya yi mata hari a lokacin da ta ke 'yar shekara 17.
Ramirez ta ce wani ɗan takarar babban kotu ya fallasa mata al'aurarsa a lokacin da suka halarci liyafa a lokacin da suke karatu a Yale a shekarun 1980.
Wanda ya kirkiro yanar gizo na duniya yana shirin kaddamar da sabuwar intanet domin ya doke Google da Facebook
Tim Berners-Lee, wanda ya kirkiro yanar gizo ya kaddamar da wani kamfanin da zai yi gogayya da Facebook, Amazon da Google.
Sabon aikin da aka yi wa fasahar, mai suna Inrupt, kamfani ne da ya samo asali daga Berners-Lee's open-source platform Solid.
Solid yana ba masu amfani damar yanke shawara ko za a adana bayanan su da kuma wanda aka ba izinin samun damar kowane bayani.
A wata hira ta musamman da aka yi da Fast Company, Berners-Lee ya yi wa'azin cewa manufar Inrupt ita ce "mulkin duniya".
"Ya kamata mu fara yanzu", in ji shi game da farawa.
"Wannan lokaci ne na tarihi.
Aikace-aikacen da ke amfani da fasahar Solid yana ba mutane damar ƙirƙirar nasu ɓangaren ajiyar bayanai na kan layi ko POD.
Zai iya ƙunsar jerin lambobin sadarwa, jerin ayyuka, kalanda, laburaren kiɗa, da sauran kayan aiki na sirri da na aiki.
Yana kama da Google Drive, Microsoft Outlook, Slack da Spotify, kuma duk suna samuwa a lokaci guda a cikin mai bincike guda.
Abin da ke na musamman game da ajiyar bayanan sirri na kan layi shi ne cewa mai amfani ne kaɗai yake zaɓan wanda zai iya samun damar kowane irin bayani.
Kamfanin ya kira wannan "karfafa ikon mutum ta hanyar bayanai".
A cewar shugaban kamfanin John Bruce, manufar Inrupt ita ce samar da albarkatu, tsari da kuma ƙwarewar da za ta sa kowa ya sami damar amfani da Solid.
Kamfanin yanzu ya ƙunshi Berners-Lee, Bruce, wani dandamali na tsaro da IBM ta saya, wasu masu haɓaka cikin gida da aka ɗauka don yin aiki a kan aikin, da kuma ƙungiyar masu shirye-shiryen shirye-shirye.
Tun daga wannan makon, masu fasahar kere-kere a duk duniya sun fara gina nasu aikace-aikacen da aka rarraba ta hanyar amfani da kayan aikin da ke cikin shafin yanar gizon Inrupt.
Berners-Lee ya ce shi da tawagarsa ba su tattauna da Facebook da Google ba game da ko za su yi canji na gaba daya da zai sauya dukkan tsarin kasuwancin su cikin dare.
Ba ma neman izininsu.
A cikin wani rubutu a kan hanyar sadarwa ta Medium da aka wallafa a ranar Asabar, Berners-Lee ya rubuta cewa imashin Inrupt shi ne samar da makamashi na kasuwanci da kuma tsarin halittu da zai taimaka wajen kare mutunci da ingancin sabon shafin da aka gina a kan dandalin Solid.
A shekara ta 1994, Berners-Lee ya canza Intanet sa'ad da ya kafa Ƙungiyar Yanar Gizo ta Duniya a Massachusetts Institute of Technology.
A cikin 'yan watannin nan, Berners-Lee ya zama mai tasiri a tattaunawar game da tsaka tsaki na yanar gizo.
Har ila yau, lokacin da ya fara Inrupt, Berners-Lee ya kasance wanda ya kafa kuma ya zama darektan World Wide Web Consortium, Gidauniyar Yanar gizo da Cibiyar Bayanai ta Bude.
"Ina ganin cewa, za a samu ci gaba mai kyau a duniyar yanar gizo", in ji Berners-Lee.
