Girgizar Kasa da Tsunami a Indonesia
A kalla mutane 384 ne suka rasa rayukansu a lokacin girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske da kuma tsunami da ta afkawa birnin Palu na kasar Indonesia ranar Juma'a, inda jami'ai suka ce ana sa ran adadin wadanda suka rasa rayukansu zai karu.
Sakamakon rashin sadarwa, jami'an agaji ba su iya samun wani bayani daga ofishin gwamnan a Donggala, yankin arewacin Palu wanda ke kusa da cibiyar girgizar kasa mai karfin 7.5.
An kwashe mutane fiye da 16,000 a Palu bayan bala'in.
Ga wasu muhimman bayanai game da Palu da Donggala a Sulawesi:
Palu shine babban birnin lardin Sulawesi ta Tsakiya, wanda ke a ƙarshen bakin tekun a gabar yamma ta tsibirin Sulawesi, tare da ƙididdigar yawan mutane 379,800 a cikin 2017.
A lokacin da girgizar ƙasa da tsunami suka addabi birnin, birnin yana bikin cika shekara 40.
Donggala wata karamar hukuma ce da ke da nisan kilomita 300 (180 miles) a gabar tekun arewa maso yammacin Sulawesi.
A cikin 2017, an kiyasta yawan mutanen Regency, yanki na yanki, ya kai 299,200.
Kifi da noma sune manyan abubuwan da ke tallafawa tattalin arzikin lardin Sulawesi ta tsakiya, musamman yankin Donggala na bakin teku.
Ma'adinan nickel ma yana da mahimmanci a lardin, amma galibi yana da ƙarfi a Morowali, a gabar tekun Sulawesi.
Hukumar kula da bala'i ta Indonesiya ta ce tsunami ya addabi Palu da Donggala sau da yawa a cikin shekaru 100 da suka shige.
A shekara ta 1938, tsunami ya kashe mutane fiye da 200 kuma ya halaka ɗarurruwan gidaje a Donggala.
Tsunami ya kuma afkawa yammacin garin Donggala a shekara ta 1996, ya kashe mutane tara.
Indonesia tana cikin yankin da ake kira Pacific Ring of Fire kuma tana fuskantar girgizar ƙasa a kai a kai.
Ga wasu daga cikin manyan girgizar ƙasa da tsunami da suka auku a cikin 'yan shekarun nan:
2004: Girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske a gabar yammacin Aceh, a lardin Indonesia, a arewacin Sumatra, ta haifar da tsunami a ranar 26 ga watan Disamba, wanda ya afkawa kasashe 14 kuma ya kashe mutane 226,000 a gabar tekun Indiya, fiye da rabin su a Aceh.
2005: A ƙarshen Maris da farkon Afrilu, an yi girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfi sosai a gabar yammacin Sumatra.
Daruruwan mutane suka mutu a tsibirin Nias da ke gabar Sumatra.
2006: Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin awo 6.8 ta afkawa kudancin Java, tsibirin da ya fi yawan jama'a a Indonesia, ta jawo tsunami da ya buge gaɓar tekun kudu, ya kashe kusan mutane 700.
2009: An yi wata girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin 7.6 kusa da birnin Padang, babban birnin lardin Yammacin Sumatra.
Mutane fiye da 1,100 suka mutu.
2010: Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin 7.5 ta afkawa tsibirin Mentawai, a waje da Sumatra, kuma ta jawo tsunami mai tsawon mita 10, wanda ya halaka ƙauyuka da yawa kuma ya kashe mutane kusan 300.
2016: Wani girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske ta afkawa gundumar Pidie Jaya a Aceh, ta haifar da bala'i da fargaba, inda mutane ke tuna da mummunan girgizar kasa da tsunami da aka yi a 2004.
Ba a yi wata annobar tsunami ba, amma mutane fiye da 100 sun mutu sa'ad da gine-gine suka rushe.
2018: Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfi ta afkawa tsibirin Lombok na Indonesiya, inda ta kashe mutane fiye da 500, mafi yawansu a arewacin tsibirin.
Girgizar ta halaka dubban gine-gine kuma ta sa dubban masu yawon buɗe ido suka makale na ɗan lokaci.
An kama ɗan fari na Sarah Palin saboda tashin hankali a gida
