An kama Palin, mai shekara 29, daga garin Wasilla, Alaska, a ranar Talata bisa zargin tashin hankali na cikin gida, tsoma baki a cikin aikin da ake yi na cin zarafin cikin gida, da kuma tsayayya da kamawa, a cewar rahoton da rundunar 'yan sanda ta jihar Alaska ta fitar a ranar Asabar.
Rahoton 'yan sanda ya ce sa'ad da wata da ta san shi ta yi ƙoƙari ta kira 'yan sanda don su kai rahoton laifin, sai ya karɓi wayarta.
Ranar Talata, a cikin wata sanarwa da aka fitar, an ce, "Mutumin da ya yi zargin ya yi wa Palin laifi ne a kotu".
Ya bayyana a kotun ranar Asabar inda ya bayyana a zaman kare kansa cewa "ba shi da laifi, tabbas", in ji gidan talabijin.
