Mahaifiyarsa Sarah Palin ta kira 'yan sanda don su kai rahoton harin.
Yanzu haka, shari'ar tana gaban kotun tsoffin sojoji na Alaska.
A watan Janairun 2016, an zarge shi da cin zarafin cikin gida, tsoma baki a cikin rahoton laifin cin zarafin cikin gida, da kuma mallakar makami yayin da yake cikin maye dangane da lamarin.
Abokinsa ya ce ya buge ta a fuska.
