Masu gabatar da kara na tarayya na neman hukuncin kisa kan wanda ake zargi da kai harin ta'addanci a birnin New York.
Masu gabatar da kara na tarayya a New York suna neman hukuncin kisa ga Sayful Saipov, wanda ake zargi da harin ta'addanci a New York wanda ya kashe mutane takwas - hukuncin da ba a taba yankewa ba a kan wani laifi na tarayya a jihar tun 1953.
An ce a ranar 31 ga watan Oktoba, Saipov mai shekara 30 ya yi amfani da motar haya ta Home Depot don kai hari a kan hanyar keke a kan titin West Side na Lower Manhattan, inda ya yi wa masu tafiya da ƙafa da kuma mai hawan keke rauni.
Bisa ga sanarwar da aka bayar game da fara shari'ar kisa a kudancin New York, idan masu gabatar da kara na son a yanke musu hukuncin kisa, dole ne su tabbatar da cewa Saipov ya "kashe" mutane takwas da gangan kuma ya "yi" da gangan da ya yi rauni mai tsanani.
An yanke hukuncin kisa a kan waɗannan laifuffuka guda biyu, kamar yadda takardar shari'a ta nuna.
Bayan 'yan makonni bayan harin, wata hukumar bincike ta kasa ta gabatar da tuhuma mai lamba 22 a kan Saipov, wadda ta hada da tuhuma guda takwas na kisan kai da kuma son yin garkuwa da mutane, da ake yawan amfani da su a wajen masu gabatar da kara a fannin aikata laifuka, da kuma na tashin hankali da kuma lalata motoci.
Harin ya bukaci "shirye-shirye mai zurfi da tunani mai kyau", in ji masu gabatar da kara, kuma sun bayyana yadda Saipov ya kai harin a matsayin "mai ban tsoro, mai zalunci da lalata".
"Sayfullo Habibullaevic Saipov ya yi wa iyalan Diego Enrique Angelini, Nicholas Cleves, Ann-Laure Decadt, Darren Drake, Ariel Erli, Hernán Ferrucci, Hernán Diego Mendoza da Alejandra Damián Pagnuccas rauni, lahani da kuma asarar abokai", in ji rahoton da aka yi.
Biyar cikin waɗanda aka kashe 'yan yawon bude ido ne daga ƙasar Argentina.
Shekara goma ke nan da aka daina yanke hukuncin kisa a gundumar Kudancin New York.
An yanke wa Khalid Barnes hukuncin kisa kan masu sayar da miyagun kwayoyi guda biyu, amma a watan Satumbar 2009 aka yanke masa hukuncin daurin rai da rai a gidan yari.
An kashe Julian da Ethel Rosenberg a 1953 a New York, bayan an yanke musu hukuncin kisa a kan laifin yin makirci da kuma leken asiri ga Tarayyar Soviet a lokacin Yakin Zamani shekaru biyu da suka gabata.
An kashe su duka a kan kujerar lantarki a ranar 19 ga Yuni, 1953.
