Ta yaya yakin cinikayya tsakanin Amurka da China zai iya zama mai kyau ga Beijing
Tashin hankalin da aka yi a farkon yakin cinikayya tsakanin Amurka da China ya yi zafi, kuma yayin da yakin bai kai karshe ba, rikici tsakanin kasashen zai iya zama da amfani ga Beijing a dogon lokaci, in ji masana.
Shugaban Amurka Donald Trump ya yi gargadin farko a farkon wannan shekarar ta hanyar sanya haraji kan kayayyakin da kasar Sin ke fitarwa ciki har da hasken rana, karfe da aluminum.
Mafi girman tashin hankali a wannan makon ya faru ne tare da sabbin tarar da suka shafi abubuwa masu daraja dala biliyan 200 (billion 150), wanda ke nuna kusan rabin dukkan kayayyakin da ke shigowa Amurka daga China.
A duk lokacin da aka yi wannan, Beijing ta yi daidai da wancan, ta ƙara haraji kashi biyar zuwa goma a kan kayayyaki da suka kai dala biliyan 60.
Kasar Sin ta yi alkawarin cewa za ta bi sahun Amurka, kuma tattalin arzikin duniya na biyu ba zai yi saurin faduwa ba.
Samun amincewar Washington zai zama kamar yin biyayya ga bukatun, amma ga shugaban kasar Sin Xi Jinping, nuna goyon bayan Amurka a fili zai zama abin kunya.
Duk da haka, masana sun ce idan Beijing ta yi wasa da kyau, matsin lamba na yaƙin cinikayya na Amurka na iya taimaka wa China ta hanyar rage dogaro da tattalin arzikin biyu.
"Gaskiyar cewa wani mataki na siyasa mai sauri a Washington ko Beijing zai iya haifar da yanayi da zai haifar da rikice-rikicen tattalin arziki a wata ƙasa, a zahiri ya fi haɗari fiye da yadda muka lura a baya", in ji Abigail Grace, mai bincike kan Asiya a cibiyar bincike ta Center for a New American Security.
